## Key Findings (to be updated throughout project)

### Confirmed Defects
1. **Clear All Tasks – No Confirmation Prompt**
   - Severity: High (Data Loss Risk)
   - Impact: Users can accidentally delete all tasks with a single click
   - Status: Documented and to be formally investigated in Check-in 2

2. **Member Since Placeholder (Profile Page)**
   - Severity: Medium (Incomplete Feature)
   - Impact: Profile page shows placeholder text instead of join date
   - Status: Identified during code review

### Missing or Unclear Requirements
- Password requirements not communicated
- Task title edit functionality not available
- Duplicate username error handling unclear

